sub_title: ★Founder at Spanish Lessons Amsterdam ★ Spanish Teacher ★ English to Spanish translator ★ Crazy human ★
summary:
In Spanish Lessons Amsterdam we believe that each student is unique and therefore, different. That's why we offer different types of lessons, so we can meet everyone's needs.
The classes are meant to be fun, easy-going and they take place in a relaxed environment while we enjoy some coffee, tea or, (why not?) some Argentinean mate so you can boost your confidence and feel comfortable enough to speak,
Mili, the founder of Spanish Lessons Amsterdam, and the rest of the team are language-passionate people who will help you get to the level you want at the pace you need.
We work with a textbook to guide us through the lessons, but also with other important resources such as newspaper articles, blogs, websites, videos, shorts, songs, extra exercises, etc, so the process of learning is always complete and diverse.
